	(text_box "ESP32-S3-WROOM-1x\n\n*In module variants that have embedded OSPI PSRAM, i.e, that embed ESP32-S3R8, pins I0136\nand Io37 are connected to OSPI PSRAM and are nott available for other uses.\n\nNote:\nESP32-S3 has four sstrapping pins:\nGP100,GP103,GP1045 and GP1046.\n\nGP100,GP1045,GP1046 are connected to the chip's internal weak pull-up/pull-down\nduring the chip reset.\n\nGP103 is floating by default\n"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 217.17 100.7516 0)
		(size 47.752 36.6624)
		(margins 0.9525 0.9525 0.9525 0.9525)
